                    "value": "<p><addressee>Mr. Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I acknowledge the<lb/> receipt of yours <date>17<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                        >th</hi></date> Inst. and<lb/> on making <sic>enquiries</sic> find that<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr. Simons</persName> paid your agent<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr. Rubenstein</persName> in <date>January<lb/> 1857</date>â€”two years\n                subscription<lb/> to the Occident to <date>March 57</date>.<lb/> and at the same\n                time paid<lb/> $8.00 for the Bible. <persName>Mr. R Hale</persName><lb/> on\n                examining his accounts<lb/> that he rendered you a statement<lb/>\n                <date>March 27<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date> of these receipts<lb/> and remitted you\n                $25.50 amount</p>"
                  },
